oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Old South Street Community Center, 1969
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the old South Street Community Center in Edgehill, November 1969. The site was within the boundaries of the Edgehill Urban Renewal Project area (Project Tenn. R-69). Photographed by Rayburn Ray of the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
